      • checkAnswersAgainstProductModel

        java.util.List<? extends ProductModelSyncIssue> checkAnswersAgainstProductModel(QuestionSet[] questionSetsToSync)
        Checks answers for the given question sets against the availability of the questions defined in the product model.
        Parameters:
        questionSetsToSync - Specific question sets for which answers will be checked. If null then an empty list of issues will be returned.
        Returns:
        a list of issues encountered
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if any of the question sets does not apply to this answer container.
